snippet.title: Scene From Catalyst Wake - "Assassins Assassinated"
snippet.description:
In this scene from The Evolving World: Catalyst Wake, Blackguard receives unexpected news from a double agent, "Oxlo", who has been reporting on ARRDO's activities.
